{"type":"message","id":"ae66c3af","parentId":"ab4870ec","timestamp":"2026-03-29T08:09:10.944Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Sun 2026-03-29 16:09 GMT+8] [Subagent Context] You are running as a subagent (depth 1/1). Results auto-announce to your requester; do not busy-poll for status.\n\n[Subagent Task]: 搜索企业数字化转型、智能安防、网络系统集成、IT运维服务等行业最新动态（2026年3月），整理3-5条关键信息，保存到 /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/memory/学习笔记.md"}],"timestamp":1774771750941}}
{"type":"message","id":"63d45bdb","parentId":"ae66c3af","timestamp":"2026-03-29T08:09:18.423Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The subagent task is to search for the latest industry news about enterprise digital transformation, intelligent security, network system integration, and IT operation services (March 2026), organize 3-5 key pieces of information, and save them to /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/memory/学习笔记.md.\n\nLet me first read the miaoda-web-search skill to understand how to search for information.","thinkingSignature":"cc28f8cfb4d19aaecf3b8623da7edd98f41ff6a3ac5966d4cb313251828de5f3"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_nunj1qqp1lvl_1","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":117,"output":128,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":42014,"totalTokens":42259,"cost":{"input":0.0000351,"output":0.0001536,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.00504168,"total":0.00523038}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774771750943}}
{"type":"message","id":"154a56e7","parentId":"63d45bdb","timestamp":"2026-03-29T08:09:18.434Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_nunj1qqp1lvl_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\r\nname: miaoda-web-search\r\ndescription: \"ALWAYS use this skill FIRST when you need to find, look up, or verify ANY information from the internet — do NOT guess URLs and fetch them directly. Provides necessary command usage instructions for keyword-based web search with AI-generated summaries. 触发词：搜索, 网页搜索, 搜一下, 查一下, 查询, 了解, 找一下, 帮我看看, web search, look up, find out, search, 搜索摘要, 查资料, 搜索引擎, 最新信息, 最近动态\"\r\noverride-tools:\r\n  - web_search\r\n---\r\n\r\n# Web Search\r\n\r\n通过 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary` 按关键词搜索互联网信息，由 AI 自动总结。\r\n\r\n## Quick Reference\r\n\r\n| 参数 | 说明 | 必需 | 默认值 |\r\n|------|------|------|--------|\r\n| `--query` | 搜索关键词（1-500 字符） | 是 | - |\r\n| `--output, -o` | 输出格式: text/json | 否 | text |\r\n\r\n## 命令选择决策树\r\n\r\n```\r\n用户想获取互联网信息\r\n├─ 有具体 URL → miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n├─ 无具体 URL，需搜索 → miaoda-studio-cli search-summary\r\n└─ 先搜索再深入 → search-summary 获取 URL → web-crawl 提取详情（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 使用示例\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# 按关键词搜索\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"React 19 新特性\"\r\n\r\n# 搜索并获取 JSON 输出\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"ByteDance 开源项目\" --output json\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Common Mistakes\r\n\r\n| 错误 | 正确做法 |\r\n|------|----------|\r\n| 无具体 URL 时用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl` | 无 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary`，有 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl`（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill） |\r\n| 搜索关键词超过 500 字符 | 提炼核心关键词，保持精简 |\r\n| 需要后续程序处理结果但未加 `--output json` | 需要解析结果时始终加 `--output json` |\r\n| 命令失败后不检查退出码 | 退出码 `1` 表示失败，检查参数和网络后重试 |\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774771758431}}
